item.description:
Join us for a celebration of epic proportions! The New England Liberty LOVE Fest is a celebration and opportunity for like minded people to educate, learn, inspire, and enjoy the best of the best in art and music.

Presale tickets and information at: http://www.libertylovefest.com/

From the Facebook event page: http://www.facebook.com/events/254668097953671/ (Please RSVP there so they can get an accurate head count).

Featured Artists include:
Jordan page
Tatiana Moroz
Heistclick
Chris Ross
Federal Crime
Leaders Led
Randy Robbins
Political Animals
Rebel Inc
Farmstand
Prince Vega
A Minor Revolution
Next to Nothing
Comatose
the Stilts
A Boy Named Sue

* Liberty LOVE Productions has no affiliation to the Ron Paul for President Campaign or any delegates. We are here to promote the pursuit of Life, Liberty, Happiness and of course: LOVE! Please stay tuned for upcoming lectures, art auctions, and more great music.
